<help general follow>

When you follow someone, you will attempt to follow them where
ever they go.  Whoever you follow can group you if they wish. 

syntax:  follow		Makes you follow yourself.
	 follow Grock	You now follow Grock.
<color=red>
See Also:  group, ungroup, order
</color>
Note:  If you stop following a leader of a group, then you are 
	automatically removed from the group.
</help>
